305
00:23:47,460 --> 00:23:52,590
<i>Ooh, full-bellied ZENKAI power!</i>

306
00:23:55,300 --> 00:24:00,590
<i>Come on out, full-on ZENKAI power!</i>

307
00:24:12,020 --> 00:24:13,860
